build instructions

required:
flex 2.6.4 (other versions might work)
bison 3.1 (other versions might work)


LINUX

run flex:

flex -o scanner.cc scanner.ll

---------------------------------------------

run bison:

win_bison -o parser.cc parser.yy

---------------------------------------------

build executable:

mkdir build
cd build
cmake ../
make install

---------------------------------------------

WINDOWS

run flex:

win_flex --wincompat -o scanner.cc scanner.ll

---------------------------------------------

run bison:

win_bison -o parser.cc parser.yy

---------------------------------------------

build executable:

md build
cd build
cmake -G "NMake Makefiles" ../
nmake install

---------------------------------------------

Running the binary:

cd bin
calc.exe input.txt
>42
